title: Do not honor
description: The card issuer is declining the transaction for an unspecified reason. The customer should contact their card issuer.

title: Invalid card number
description: The card number entered is invalid. Verify the card number and try again.

title: Insufficient funds
description: The card has insufficient funds to complete the transaction.

title: Expired card
description: The card has expired. The customer needs to use a different card.

title: Exceeds withdrawal limit
description: The transaction amount exceeds the card's withdrawal limit.

title: Invalid transaction
description: The transaction type is invalid for this card or merchant.

title: Issuer unavailable
description: The card issuer is temporarily unavailable. Try the transaction again later.

title: Insufficient funds
description: The bank account has insufficient funds for the ACH transaction.

title: Account closed
description: The bank account has been closed.

title: No account/unable to locate account
description: The bank account number does not correspond to an existing account.

title: Invalid account number
description: The bank account number is not valid.

title: Unauthorized debit to consumer account
description: The account holder has not authorized this debit transaction.

title: Payment stopped
description: The account holder has placed a stop payment on this transaction.

title: Originator not known
description: The originator of the transaction is not known to the account holder.

title: Representative payee deceased
description: The representative payee is deceased or unable to continue in that capacity.

title: Account frozen
description: The bank account is frozen and cannot accept transactions.
